v0.6 - Nov. 22, 2010
 - Changed the URL for the libvirt source to reflect Red Hat's change.

v0.5 - Nov. 22, 2010
 - Minor textual changes to add a missing line that should have been displayed
   to the user.

v0.4 - Nov. 22, 2010
 - Added the following packages to the dependency list as they were needed on
   a "minimal" install server.
   - dnsmasq
   - iscsi-initiator-utils
   - lvm2

v0.3 - Nov. 22, 2010
 - Fixed the 'depmod' section by chdir'ing to the kernel directory before
   calling depmod.
 - Minor display cleanup.

v0.2 - Nov. 22, 2010
 - Switched the install order to build and install the hypervisor before
   libvirt.
 - Disabled the check for the check of the kernel module binary as it was found
   before it ran the compile for the first time. Will re-enable when a suitable
   file is found.
   
v0.1 - Nov. 22, 2010
 - First release.
